Problem
In the last decade the sport of rowing really took off at a hight school level. It is recognized as beeing a great vehicle for students-athletes to get into great colleges. 
However to become a great rowing team member takes a lot of individual, presonalized tranining. 


Solution: 
Elite rowing LLC  focuses on individual and personalized training programs for children, as young 10 years old. Their focus is on establishing good foundations, develop  efficient technics and then building stregth and speed. 
Elite rowing LLC needs a parent friendly webside that encopasses all the expertise they have to offer. 
